eparin and non-steroidal analgesics after total hip replacement?" Ann R Coll Surg Engl 77 (1995):  395[4] "Product Information. Orgaran (danaparoid)." Organon  (2001):[5] "Product Information. Normiflo (ardeparin)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories  (2001):[6] "Product Information. Innohep (tinzaparin)." DuPont Pharmaceuticals  (2001):[7] "Product Information. Arixtra (fondaparinux)." Organon  (2002):', 1767363027);
